 Two types of Export/Import

Default Export/Import
export default Component; import Component from "path";

- Named Export/Import
export const Component; import {Component} from "path";

React Hooks
(Normal JS utility functions)

-useState() - Superpowerful State Variables in react
whenever state variables update, react triggers a reconciliation cycle(re-renders the component)
-useEffect()- if no dependency array => useEffect is called on every render
if dependency array is empty = [] => useEffect called on every Initial render(just once).
if dependency array is [btnNamereact] => called everytime btnnamereact is updated.
# 2 types Routing in Web Apps
Clent side Routing- first time only it load all components and it will route to clicked word Single page application(is client side routing)
server side Routing- make network call fetch api and route the page



